Package: RcppOctave
Type: Package
Title: Seamless Interface to Octave -- and Matlab
Version: 0.6.2
Date: 2011-06-07
Author: Renaud Gaujoux
Maintainer: Renaud Gaujoux <renaud@cbio.uct.ac.za>
Description: Seamless Interface to Octave. The primary goal
    is to be facilitate the port of Matlab/Octave scripts
    to R. Allow to call any Octave functions and browse
    their documentation from R, pass variables between R
    and Octave, use R core RNGs in Octave.
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: http://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/rcppoctave/
LazyLoad: yes
SystemRequirements: Octave (>=3.2.4)
Depends:
    methods,
    Rcpp (>= 0.9.4)
Suggests:
    RUnit,
    stringr,
    devtools
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Collate:
	'devutils.R'
    'utils.R'
    'package.R'
    'interface.R'
    'Octave-class.R'
    'OctaveFunction-class.R'
    'base-functions.R'
    'eval.R'
    'random.R'
